---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About ByteLite - A Different Architecture for Compression"
  description="Classical compression peaked. ByteLite is an engineered attempt to push past it ‚Äî dictionary cascades, Szudzik pairing, shared models. Deep Kore asks: what if this architecture is a blueprint for more than storage?"
  keywords={["ByteLite mission", "dictionary cascade compression", "frontier compression", "Tash Broadwater", "compression technology", "Deep Kore research", "Hutter Prize compression"]}
  schemaType="AboutPage"
>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Origin Story -->
      <div id="story" class="story-section">
        <h2>The HeartStrings Discovery</h2>
        <div class="story-content">
          <p class="lead">
            In 2024, while developing HeartStrings, an AI-powered dating platform,
            founder Tash Broadwater encountered a fundamental challenge: AI models demanded excessive data
            storage and computing resources, limiting innovation for independent developers.
          </p>

          <blockquote>
            "What if the problem isn't the AI‚Äîbut the way we represent information?"
          </blockquote>

          <p>
            That question became ByteLite. Not a better compressor ‚Äî a different kind of compressor.
            Dictionary cascades. Szudzik pairing. Shared-model assumptions.
            We're building toward ratios that would make the current enwik9 leaders look bloated.
            Hutter Prize submission planned. Verification will tell us how close we actually get.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission & Vision -->
      <div class="mission-section">
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>
            To democratize access to advanced computation by making data storage and transmission 
            virtually free, enabling innovation at every scale.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>
            Storage and bandwidth shouldn't be the limiting factor.
            ByteLite is our attempt to remove that bottleneck for structured data.
            Deep Kore is our bet that the same architecture might matter for more than just storage.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Current Status -->
      <div class="status-section">
        <h2>Project Status</h2>
        <div class="status-grid">
          <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>ByteLite Compression</h3>
              <span class="status-badge ready">Active Development</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Dictionary-cascade architecture in advanced development. Patent US 63/807,027 filed.
              Hutter Prize submission planned. Engineering toward extreme compression ratios on
              structured data. ByteLite Application Demo in preparation. Enterprise licensing
              discussions underway.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 85%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>Genesis Goal Keeper</h3>
              <span class="status-badge complete">Active</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Safety framework operational. Guides all Deep Kore research under responsible
              development protocols. Provides constraint enforcement and ethical guardrails
              for blueprint-stage intelligence research.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill deepkore" style="width: 100%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>Deep Kore</h3>
              <span class="status-badge development">Research Phase</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              What if extreme compression and intelligence share the same math?
              Deep Kore is our attempt to find out. Blueprint-stage architecture.
              Genesis Goal Keeper safety framework. We're building carefully because
              we're building toward something that might actually matter.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill deepkore" style="width: 35%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-header">
              <h3>HeartStrings</h3>
              <span class="status-badge on-hold">On Hold</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              The AI-powered dating platform that sparked ByteLite's discovery. Development paused
              as solo developer Tash Broadwater prioritizes Hutter Prize submission. HeartStrings
              will resume as the first consumer application to leverage ByteLite's compression
              technology for efficient AI model deployment.
            </p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill heartstrings" style="width: 40%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Deep Kore Philosophy -->
      <div class="philosophy-section">
        <h2>Deep Kore: Compression as a Map to Something Bigger</h2>
        <p class="philosophy-intro">
          The math that compresses data might also be the math that organizes thought.
          Deep Kore is our physics-inspired attempt to find out. We're not claiming we've built AGI.
          We're claiming we've found an architecture worth building toward.
        </p>

        <div class="philosophy-principles">
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">üî¨</span>
            <h4>Efficient Architecture</h4>
            <p>Doing more with less ‚Äî that's what compression teaches us</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">üåä</span>
            <h4>Recursive Depth</h4>
            <p>Structures that go deeper than classical architectures dare</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">‚ùì</span>
            <h4>Open Questions</h4>
            <p>How far does this go? We're building to find out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder -->
      <div class="founder-section">
        <h2>Leadership</h2>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <h3>Tash Broadwater, Founder & CEO</h3>
          <p>
            Compression researcher and software engineer with 15+ years optimizing data systems. 
            Specializes in algorithmic design and edge AI systems. When traditional solutions fail, 
            Tash builds new ones from scratch‚ÄîByteLite is the result of that ethos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h3>Join Our Journey</h3>
        <p>ByteLite early access. Deep Kore research updates. We're building something different.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe for Updates</a>
          <a href="/licensing" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Licensing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .story-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .story-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  /* Status Section */
  .status-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .status-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .status-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .status-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .status-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .status-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .status-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .status-badge {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .status-badge.ready {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .status-badge.complete {
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2);
    color: #A855F7;
    border: 1px solid #A855F7;
  }

  .status-badge.development {
    background: rgba(255, 171, 0, 0.2);
    color: #FFAB00;
    border: 1px solid #FFAB00;
  }

  .status-badge.on-hold {
    background: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.2);
    color: #999999;
    border: 1px solid #999999;
  }

  .status-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    height: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), #00A8CC);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .progress-fill.deepkore {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #A855F7, #FF006E);
  }

  .progress-fill.heartstrings {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF006E, #FFAB00);
  }

  .progress-fill::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3),
      transparent
    );
    animation: shimmer 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(-100%);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(100%);
    }
  }

  .mission-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .mission-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Philosophy Section */
  .philosophy-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .philosophy-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.5);
  }

  .philosophy-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .philosophy-principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .principle {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .principle .icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .principle h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .principle p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  /* Founder Section */
  .founder-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .founder-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .founder-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .founder-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #00B8E6;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-section h2,
    .status-section h2,
    .philosophy-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .status-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .status-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .philosophy-section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>